---
import { site } from '@/lib/site';
import { getPostUrl } from '@/lib/posts';
const { post } = Astro.props;
const url = getPostUrl(post);
---
<section class="post-extra-card">
  <div class="post-copyright">
    <div class="copyright-title"><i class="fas fa-copyright"></i> 文章版权</div>
    <p><strong>作者：</strong>{site.author}</p>
    <p><strong>链接：</strong><a href={url}>{url}</a></p>
    <p><strong>声明：</strong>本文采用 <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.zh-hans" target="_blank">CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</a> 协议，转载请注明出处。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="comment-placeholder" id="comments">
    <div>
      <i class="far fa-comments"></i>
      <strong>评论区预留</strong>
      <p>正式切换前可选择 Giscus / Gitalk / Twikoo。当前预览版暂不接入第三方脚本，避免干扰主站。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
